<div id="review_112590581" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/112590581" />
    <a title="Jake" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1401909-jake"><img alt="Jake" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1356911477p2/1401909.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/112590581?book_show_action=true">Jul 20, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jake" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jake" href="/user/show/1401909-jake">Jake</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1401909-jake?shelf=miscellany">miscellany</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1401909-jake?shelf=espionage">espionage</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer112590581" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3457229765182214810">A well told Roman a clef about unlikely espionage in the 1980s. Basichis does a great job of recounting events that happened behind the veil of how the world does espionage (in ways that the public is willfully ignorant of). His writing is a bit stilted at times and the stories can seem to be strung together without rhythm. Nevertheless, it is a good book that should be read by anyone interested in espionage. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

