  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/75322693?book_show_action=true">Oct 21, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Florence" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Florence" href="/user/show/1649751-florence">Florence</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer75322693" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer395854307560902858">This book takes you inside the bizarre and shadowy world of espionage. Events take place in a parallel universe where ordinary things suddenly take on a sinister meaning. Frighteningly believable.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


